thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Jamie Spitty

author: Jamie Spitty
title: Jamie Spitty
text: I recently ordered headphones off the storedj website which arrived broken which was the manufactures fault. I called storedj to organise a replacement and was helped by Stian who ran through a bunch of different headphones with me to find a pair i was happy with :) would definitly recommend 10/10
